      "text": "「うぅ～ん……お母様ぁ……\nおしりペンペンは勘弁してくださいまし～」だって！",
      "startTime": 10.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すずらしいな……ん？　電話か？",
      "startTime": 17.800000159,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
