    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お母さんだ。ごめんね、ちょっといい？",
      "startTime": 21.8666686058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし？　うん、うん、大丈夫だよ\n今{user}さんとお話してた",
      "startTime": 31.86666797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、うん……え？\nえーーーーーー！？",
      "startTime": 39.9333346367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
